text: Erlenmoos is a municipality in Biberach in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. It is near Ochsenhausen. The mayor of Erlenmoos is Marcus Schmid since 2022. About 1,000 people live there. The villages of Edenbachen, Eichbühl and Oberstetten are parts of Erlenmoos. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Biberach (district)
